title: Trina Interview
itunes:title: Trina Interview
description:
Today on the show we had the baddest chick in the building Trina! She spoke about her new album, past relationships and her most recent, and she made it clear that even if your cool with her, you can get shaded on too. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to an Uber Eats Driver that was caught masturbating outside a woman's house. Also we had BET Vice President Connie Orlando stop by who spoke about the upcoming BET awards, shows coming to BET and more.
